 collaborate and share Keynote presentations with Keynote on the web. Changes will sync across your devices with iCloud.","Mail.Application.Title":"iCloud Mail - Apple iCloud","Mail.IndexFile.Meta.Description":"View and send mail from your iCloud email address on the web. Sign in or create a new account to get started.","Notes.Application.Title":"Notes - Apple iCloud","Notes.IndexFile.Meta.Description":"View, edit, create and share your notes with Notes on the web. Changes will sync across your devices with iCloud.","Numbers.Application.Title":"Numbers - Apple iCloud","Numbers.IndexFile.Meta.Description":"Create, edit, collaborate and share spreadsheets with Numbers on the web. Changes will sync across your devices with iCloud.","Pages.Application.Title":"Pages - Apple iCloud","Pages.IndexFile.Meta.Description":"Create, edit, collaborate and share documents with Pages on the web. Changes will sync across your devices with iCloud.","Photos.Application.Title":"iCloud Photos - Apple iCloud","Photos.IndexFile.Meta.Description":"View, organize, and share photos and videos with iCloud Photos on the web. Changes will sync across your devices with iCloud.","Plan.Application.Title":"iCloud Plan - Apple iCloud","Plan.IndexFile.Meta.Description":"Learn about iCloud+ plans and choose what’s right for you. Compare prices, storage, access to premium features and more.","Recovery.Application.Title":"iCloud Recovery - Apple iCloud","Recovery.IndexFile.Meta.Description":"Recover files deleted from both iCloud Drive and other apps within the last 30 days, or restore an earlier version of your Calendar, Contacts and Safari bookmarks.","Reminders.Application.Title":"Reminders - Apple iCloud","Reminders.IndexFile.Meta.Description":"Create and view your reminders with Reminders on the web. Changes will sync across your devices with iCloud.","Settings.Application.Title":"Settings - Apple iCloud","Settings.IndexFile.Meta.Description":"Easily update your Apple Account information and personalize your iCloud plan and settings. Get quick access to helpful links and more.","Storage.Application.Title":"Storage - Apple iCloud","Storage.IndexFile.Meta.Description":"Log in to iCloud.com to view your iCloud Storage usage, check your family’s usage and learn how to upgrade.","Invites.Application.Title":"Apple Invites - Apple iCloud","Invites.IndexFile.Meta.Description":"Create online party invitations - for birthdays, graduations, baby showers & more. Track RSVPs, create shared albums, and send instantly by email or text.","AccountMenuPopover.Settings":"Account Settings","AccountMenuPopover.ManageAppleId":"Manage Apple Account","AccountMenuPopover.SignOut":"Sign Out","VoiceOver.Menu.Close":"Close menu","VoiceOver.Close":"Close","AccountMenuPopover.Button.AriaLabel":"Account","AccountTilePopover.Button.Text":"There was a problem loading your Apple Account picture.","HelpMenu.UserGuide":"iCloud User Guide","HelpMenu.AriaLabel":"Apple Support Page (opens in new tab)","IDMSAuthWidget.SignInLabel":"Sign in to iCloud","VoiceOver.HomePage":"iCloud.com Home Page","VoiceOver.HomePage.CustomizationMode":"Customizing Home Page: iCloud.com Home Page","ProfileCard.PlanType.MAID":"Managed Apple Account","ProfileCard.PlanType.WebOnly":"iCloud Web-Only","ProfileCard.PlanType.Standard":"iCloud","ProfileCard.PlanType.Plus":"iCloud+","VoiceOver.ProfileCard.Heading":"Account Information","Avatar.ImageAlt":"Your profile Image","ImagePicker.CancelButtonLabel":"Cancel","ImagePicker.DoneButtonLabel":"Save","ImagePicker.CompactDoneButtonLabel":"Save Changes","ImagePicker.ChangeImageButtonLabel":"Browse your device for a new image…","ImagePicker.Alert.Title.UnsupportedFileType":"Invalid Image Format","ImagePicker.Alert.Title.FileTooLarge":"Could Not Upload Photo","ImagePicker.Alert.Title.Generic":"Could Not Upload Photo","ImagePicker.Alert.Description.UnsupportedFileType":"Make sure the format of your photo is JPEG, GIF, PNG, or BMP.","ImagePicker.Alert.Description.FileTooLarge":"The image you are trying to upload is too large. Maximum file size allowed is 10 MB.","ImagePicker.Alert.Description.Generic":"Please try again.","ImagePicker.Alert.Action.Ok":"OK","ImagePicker.Instructions":"To replace your Apple Account photo, drag an image onto the box or browse your device.","ImagePicker.Title":"Change Apple Account Photo","ImagePicker.ErrorImageFailedToLoad":"Couldn’t load the image","ImagePicker.DropZoneLabel":"Drop Here","ImagePicker.ZoomControl.ZoomLabel":"Zoom","ImagePicker.RotationControl.RotateLabel":"Rotate","VoiceOver.ImagePicker.ZoomControl.ZoomControlAriaLabel":"Adjust zoom level","VoiceOver.ImagePicker.RotationControl.RotateLabel":"Rotate","VoiceOver.ImagePicker.LoadingAriaLabel":"Loading image","VoiceOver.ImagePicker.CloseButtonLabel":"Cancel","HomeTile.Loading":"Loading","HomeTile.NotLoaded":"—","HomeTile.Error":"Error","VoiceOver.HomeTile.LoadingComplete":"Loading Complete","VoiceOver.HomeTile.LongPressOpenQuickAction":"Long press to open quick action menu.","VoiceOver.QuickActionMenu.ButtonAriaLabel":"%{actionLabel}. Quick action button for item %{tileRowSummaryAriaLabel}","Tile.Edit":"Edit","VoiceOver.Tile.EditAriaLabel":"Edit %{tileName} tile","VoiceOver.Tile.RemoveAriaLabel":"Remove %{tileName} tile","ErrorHomeTileContent.Message":"There was a problem loading this content.","ErrorHomeTileContent.TryAgain":"Try Again","ErrorHomeTileContent.OpenApp":"Open %{appName}","DeletedErrorTileContent.Mail.Message":"Previously selected folder has been deleted.","DeletedErrorTileContent.Reminders.Message":"Previously selected list has been deleted.","DeletedErrorTileContent.Drive.Message":"Previously selected folder has been deleted.","DeletedErrorTileContent.Photos.Message":"Previously selected album has been deleted.","DeletedErrorTileContent.Notes.Message":"Previously selected folder has been deleted.","DeletedErrorTileContent.Calendar.Message":"Previously selected calendar has been deleted.","DeletedErrorTileContent.Calendar.Multiple.Messag