alContent.ListDescription.BulletPointThree":"If you have shared calendars, all sharing information is removed when you restore them. You’ll need to share your calendars again, and ask other people to reinvite you to share their calendars.","RecoveryPage.CalendarArchivesRecoveryTileWrapper.Confirmation.Title":"Restore Calendars?","RecoveryPage.CalendarArchivesRecoveryTileWrapper.Confirmation.Description":"The archive you selected will replace the calendars on all your devices. Your current calendars will be archived. Changes made to calendars while restoration is in progress won’t be saved. Wait until it’s finished before making changes.","RecoveryPage.CalendarArchivesRecoveryTileWrapper.Confirmation.RestoreButton":"Restore","RecoveryPage.CalendarArchivesRecoveryTileWrapper.AlertSuccess.Title":"Calendars Restored","RecoveryPage.CalendarArchivesRecoveryTileWrapper.AlertSuccess.Description":"Your calendars were successfully restored at %{time}. Restored calendars will appear on all your devices.","RecoveryPage.CalendarArchivesRecoveryTileWrapper.AlertFailure.Title":"Couldn’t Restore Calendars","RecoveryPage.CalendarArchivesRecoveryTileWrapper.AlertFailure.Description":"Calendars syncing has been disabled because of an error. Contact iCloud Support for assistance.","RecoveryPage.ContactArchivesRecoveryTileWrapper.Confirmation.Title":"Restore Contacts?","RecoveryPage.ContactArchivesRecoveryTileWrapper.Confirmation.Description":"The archive you selected will replace the contacts on all your devices. Your current contacts will be archived. Changes made to contacts while restoration is in progress won’t be saved. Wait until it’s finished before making changes.","RecoveryPage.ContactArchivesRecoveryTileWrapper.Confirmation.RestoreButton":"Restore","RecoveryPage.ContactArchivesRecoveryTileWrapper.AlertSuccess.Title":"Contacts Restored","RecoveryPage.ContactArchivesRecoveryTileWrapper.AlertSuccess.Description":"Your contacts were successfully restored at %{time}. Restored cont