d and saved only with the Reminders app on your Apple devices.","RemindersTemplatePage.Description.Unsupported":"List templates can be previewed and saved only with the Reminders app on Apple devices running at least iOS 16, iPadOS 16, or macOS 13.","Drive.Icon.Description.Key":"Keynote Presentation","Drive.Icon.Description.Numbers":"Numbers Spreadsheet","Drive.Icon.Description.Pages":"Pages Document","Drive.Icon.Description.PowerPoint":"PowerPoint Presentation","Drive.Icon.Description.Excel":"Excel Spreadsheet","Drive.Icon.Description.Word":"Word Document","Drive.Icon.Description.Pdf":"PDF","Drive.Icon.Description.Default":"Item","Drive.Icon.Description.Archive":"ZIP Archive","Drive.Icon.Description.Image":"%{fileExtension} Image","Drive.Icon.Description.Audio":"%{fileExtension} Audio","Drive.Icon.Description.Video":"%{fileExtension} Video","HomePage.CustomizeDashboard":"Customize","VoiceOver.CustomizeDashboard.OpeningPage":"Now showing Home Page Customization","VoiceOver.CustomizeDashboard.ClosingPage":"Now showing Home Page","HomePage.CustomizeDashboard.Header.Heading":"Home Page Customization","HomePage.CustomizeDashboard.Header.Button.ChangeWallpaper":"Change Wallpaper","HomePage.CustomizeDashboard.Header.Button.AddTile":"Add Tile","HomePage.CustomizeDashboard.Header.Button.ShowTips":"Show Tips","HomePage.CustomizeDashboard.Header.Button.Done":"Done","HomePage.CustomizeDashboard.Header.Button.EditBackground":"Select Background Color","HomePage.CustomizeDashboard.AddButton.AriaLabel":"Add a new tile to the dashboard","HomePage.CustomizeDashboard.AddedTile.AriaLabel":"Added %{tileName} tile","HomePage.CustomizeDashboard.RemoveButton.AriaLabel":"Remove the %{tileName} tile from the dashboard","HomePage.CustomizeDashboard.RemovedTile.AriaLabel":"Removed %{tileName} tile","HomePage.CustomizeDashboard.TilePicker.Label":"Which tile do you want to use?","HomePage.CustomizeDashboard.TilePicker.Add.Label":"Which tile do you want to add?","HomePage.CustomizeDashboard.Tile