ngs.LookMeUpByEmail.Modal.List.Title.Many":"%{appsCount} Apps","AccountPage.Settings.LookMeUpByEmail.Modal.List.Title.One":"1 App","AccountPage.Settings.LookMeUpByEmail.Modal.List.Title.Two":"2 Apps","AccountPage.Settings.LookMeUpByEmail.Modal.List.Empty.Title":"No Apps","AccountPage.Settings.LookMeUpByEmail.Modal.List.Empty.Content":"You can prevent any listed app from showing your name and email address to other users by deselecting the app’s checkbox.","AccountPage.Settings.LookMeUpByEmail.Modal.List.Description":"You can prevent any listed app from showing your name and email address to other users by deselecting the app’s checkbox.","VoiceOver.AccountPage.LookMeUpByEmail.Modal.List.AriaLabel":"List of apps","VoiceOver.AccountPage.LookMeUpByEmail.Modal.List.Checkbox.AriaLbel":"whether %{appName} can show your name and email to other users","AccountPage.Settings.Access.Title":"Sign Out of All Browsers","AccountPage.Settings.Access.Button.Name":"Sign Out of All Browsers","AccountPage.Settings.Access.Description":"Immediately sign out of all browsers currently signed in to iCloud.com with this Apple Account.","AccountPage.Settings.Access.Signout.Modal.Title":"Sign Out of All Browsers?","AccountPage.Settings.Access.Signout.Modal.Description":"Are you sure you want to sign out of iCloud on all browsers? You will be asked to verify your identity the next time you sign in.","AccountPage.Settings.Access.Signout.Cancel":"Cancel","AccountPage.Settings.Access.Signout.Confirm":"Sign Out","AccountPage.AppleId.Title":"Apple Account","AccountPage.Settings.Photo.Title":"Photo","AccountPage.Settings.Photo.ChangeAppleIDPhoto.Button.Name":"Change Apple Account Photo","AccountPage.Settings.AppleID.Title":"Apple Account Settings","AccountPage.Settings.AppleID.Description":"Review or update important information like your name, password, and security details. See how others can reach you, check your payment information, and manage the devices connected to your account.","AccountPage.Settings.AppleID.Button.Name":"account.apple.com","AccountPage.Settings.FindDevices.Title":"Find Your Devices","AccountPage.Settings.FindDevices.Description":"Find your iPhone, iPad, Mac, Apple Watch, AirPods, or Beats. Or help locate Family Sharing devices.","AccountPage.Settings.FindDevices.Button.Name":"Find Devices","VoiceOver.AccountPage.PlanCard":"iCloud plan, storage and links to other pages.","AccountPage.Settings.ChangeNotificationSettings.Title":"Browser Notifications for Apps","AccountPage.Settings.ChangeNotificationSettings.Description":"Receive notifications from your iCloud apps also when you don’t have an iCloud.com page open.","AccountPage.Settings.ChangeNotificationSettings.Button.Label":"Manage Browser Notifications","AccountPage.Settings.ChangeNotificationSettings.NotSupported.Description":"iCloud.com notifications are not currently supported on this device.","AccountPage.Settings.ChangeNotificationSettings.NotSupported.Button.Label":"Learn more","UpgradePlanTiles.Upgrade":"Upgrade to iCloud+","UpgradePlanTiles.Upgrade.Description":"When you upgrade to iCloud+ you get the storage you need plus premium features to protect your privacy.","UpgradePlanTiles.MoreStorage":"More Storage","UpgradePlanTiles.MoreStorage.Description":"Choose the amount of storage that’s right for you. iCloud+ plans include 50 GB, 200 GB, 2 TB, 6 TB or 12 TB of storage.","UpgradePlanTiles.MoreStorage.LinkText":"Learn more about iCloud+ Plans and Pricing","UpgradePlanTiles.MoreStorage.ImageAlt":"Bar graph displaying the storage options for iCloud+ plans, which are 50 GB, 200 GB, and 2 TB","UpgradePlanTiles.PrivateRelay":"iCloud Private Relay","UpgradePlanTiles.PrivateRelay.Description":"Use iCloud Private Relay on your iPhone, iPad, iPod touch, and Mac to hide your IP address and browsing activity in Safari and protect your unencrypted internet traffic.","UpgradePlanTiles.PrivateRelay.LinkText":"Learn more about Private Relay","UpgradePlanTiles.HideMyEmail":"Hide My Email","UpgradePlanTiles.HideMyEmail.Description":"Create unique, random email addresses that forward to your inbox so you can send and receive email without having to share your personal email address.","UpgradePlanTiles.HideMyEmail.LinkText":"Learn more about Hide My Email","UpgradePlanTiles.HideMyEmail.ImageAlt":"iPhone showing a sign-up page for Nike membership with an overlay titled ‘Hide My Email’ with a randomized email address and a ‘Continue’ button","UpgradePlanTiles.HomeKitSecureVideo":"HomeKit Secure Video","UpgradePlanTiles.HomeKitSecureVideo.Description":"Connect your home security cameras in the Home App so you can record and view the footage from anywhere. It’s private, secure, and doesn’t use your iCloud storage.","UpgradePlanTiles.HomeKitSecureVideo.LinkText":"Learn more about HomeKit Secure Video","UpgradePlanTiles.CustomEmailDomain":"Custom Email Domain","UpgradePlanTiles.CustomEmailDomain.Description":"Personalize your iCloud Mail address with a custom domain name. You can even invite your family and friends to use the same domain with their iCloud Mail accounts.","UpgradePlanTiles.CustomEmailDomain.LinkText":"Learn more about Custom Email Domain","UpgradePlanTiles.FamilySharing":"Family Sharing","UpgradePlanTiles.FamilySharing.Description":"Share your iCloud+ plan with up to five family members so that everyone gets extra storage and premium features. Each family member uses their own Apple Account, so everyone’s content stays private.","UpgradePlanTiles.FamilySharing.LinkText":"Learn more about iCloud+ Family Sharing","UpgradePlanTiles.Beta":"BETA","Breadcrumbs":"Breadcrumbs","Alert.OkButton":"OK","Alert.CancelButton":"Cancel","Alert.ContactSupport":"iCloud Support","AppSwitcherOnboardingPopover.QuickAccess.Title":"Quick Access","AppSwitcherOnboardingPopover.QuickAccess.Content":"Go directly to an app, review your plan and storage usage, or learn more about iCloud features.","AppSwitcherOnboardingPopover.Customize.Title":"Customize","AppSwitcherOnboardingPopover.Customize.Content":"Choose the apps you want to see on your home page.","AppSwitcherOnboardingPopover.CloseButton.AriaLabel":"Close Tip","UnsupportedApps.Mobile":"To use %{appName} on iCloud.com, switch to a tablet or desktop browser.","UnsupportedApps.Tablet":"To use %{appName} on iCloud.com, switch to a desktop browser.","UnsupportedApps.HomePageButton":"iCloud Home Page","StaticPages.UnsupportedSafariVersionTabGroups.Message":"Upgrade to Safari 16 or later to use shared Tab Groups.","StaticPages.EnableCookies.Message":"To use iCloud, enable cookies in your browser, then try again.","StaticPages.UnsupportedBrowserTabGroups.Message":"Shared Tab Groups are only available on Safari 16 or later.","StaticPages.UnsupportedMobile.Message":"Your browser is not currently supported.","StaticPages.UnsupportedMobile.SubMessage":"You may be able to use iCloud with the mail, contacts, and calendar apps on your device.","StaticPages.WebsiteUnavailable.Message":"iCloud.com is not available in your country or region.","StaticPages.UnsupportedBrowser.Message":"Your browser is not supported.","StaticPages.UnsupportedBrowser.SubMessage":"To use iCloud, we recommend using the latest version of Safari, Firefox, Microsoft Edge, or Chrome.","StaticPages.NotFound.Message":"iCloud can’t find that page.","StaticPages.LearnMore":"Learn more","StaticPages.TryAgain":"Try again","StaticPages.HomePage":"iCloud Home Page","RemoveTileAlert.Title":"Remove “%{tileName}” Tile?","RemoveTileAlert.Description":"Removing this tile will not delete any data. You can still go directly to %{tileName} from the quick access menu.","RemoveTileAlert.Cancel":"Cancel","RemoveTileAlert.Remove":"Remove","ContinueOnDevice.ContinueButton.Title":"Continue on Device…","ContinueOnDevice.ContinueButton.Title.Sending":"Sending Notification…","ContinueOnDevice.SuccessDialog.Title":"Notification Sent","ContinueOnDevice.SuccessDialog.Description.LineOne.MoreThanThree":"Look for the Settings notification on %{device1}, %{device2}, %{device3}, and %{restCount} more.","ContinueOnDevice.SuccessDialog.Description.LineOne.ThreeDevices":"Look for the Settings notification on %{device1}, %{device2}, and %{device3}.","ContinueOnDevice.SuccessDialog.Description.LineOne.TwoDevices":"Look for the Settings notification on %{device1} and %{device2}.","ContinueOnDevice.SuccessDialog.Description.LineOne.OneDevice":"Look for the Settings notification on %{device1}.","ContinueOnDevice.SuccessDialog.Description.LineTwo":"Requires a device running at least iOS 15.2, iPadOS 15.2, or macOS Monterey 12.1.","ContinueOnDevice.FailedDialog.Title":"Couldn’t Send Notification","ContinueOnDevice.FailedDialog.Description":"There was a problem sending your notification. Try again later.","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlanUpgrade.Title":"How to Change Your iCloud Plan","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlanUpgrade.Description":"Use Continue on Device to send a notification to your Apple devices that will take you directly to iCloud Plan Settings.","ContinueOnDevice.setupPrivateRelay.Title":"How to Manage Private Relay Settings","ContinueOnDevice.setupPrivateRelay.Description":"Use Continue on Device to send a notification to your Apple devices that will take you directly to Private Relay settings. You can manage Private Relay settings for each of your devices running at least iOS 15, iPadOS 15, or macOS Monterey 12.","ContinueOnDevice.homeKitSecureVideo.Title":"How to Set Up HomeKit Secure Video","ContinueOnDevice.homeKitSecureVideo.Description":"To set up HomeKit Secure Video, first enable iCloud for Home. On an iPhone or iPad, go to Settings #{chevron} %{fullName} #{chevron} iCloud and turn on Home. On a Mac, go to System Settings #{chevron} Apple Account #{chevron} iCloud, then select Home. Next, go to the Home app and turn on “Stream & Allow Recording” in Recording Options for your camera.","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.Organizer.Title":"How to Manage iCloud+ Family Sharing ","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.Organizer.Description":"Use Continue on Device to send a notification to your Apple devices that will take you directly to iCloud+ Family Sharing settings.","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.OrganizerNoFamily.Title":"How to Start Sharing with Family","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.OrganizerNoFamily.Description":"Use Continue on Device to send a notification to your Apple devices that will take you directly to Family Sharing setup.","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.Member.Title":"How to Stop Using Shared iCloud+ Plan","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.Member.Description":"Use Continue on Device to send a notification to your Apple devices that will take you directly to Shared iCloud+ Plan settings.","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudStorageManage.Title":"How to Manage Your iCloud Storage","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudStorageManage.Description":"Use Continue on Device to send a notification to your Apple devices that will take you directly to iCloud Storage Settings.","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudStorageManage.StorageFull.Title":"How to Change iCloud Plan and Add Storage","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudStorageManage.StorageFull.Description":"Use Continue on Device to send a notification to your Apple devices that will take you directly to iCloud Plan Settings.","ContinueOnDevice.NoDevice.IOS.Description":"On an iPhone, iPad, or iPod touch","ContinueOnDevice.NoDevice.Mac.Description":"On a Mac","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlanUpgrade.NoDevice.Title":"How to Change Your iCloud Plan","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlanUpgrade.NoDevice.Description":"Go to Settings #{chevron} %{fullName} #{chevron} iCloud #{chevron} Manage Account Storage #{chevron} Change Storage Plan","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlanUpgrade.NoDevice.Description2":"Go to System Settings #{chevron} Apple Account #{chevron} iCloud #{chevron} Manage… #{chevron} Change Storage Plan…","ContinueOnDevice.setupPrivateRelay.NoDevice.Title":"How to Manage Private Relay Settings for Your Device","ContinueOnDevice.setupPrivateRelay.NoDevice.Description":"Go to Settings #{chevron} %{fullName} #{chevron} iCloud #{chevron} Private Relay","ContinueOnDevice.setupPrivateRelay.NoDevice.Description2":"Go to System Settings #{chevron} Apple Account #{chevron} iCloud #{chevron} Private Relay Options","ContinueOnDevice.setupPrivateRelay.NoDevice.Notice":"Private Relay requires a device running at least iOS 15, iPadOS 15, or macOS Monterey 12.","ContinueOnDevice.homeKitSecureVideo.NoDevice.Title":"How to Set Up HomeKit Secure Video","ContinueOnDevice.homeKitSecureVideo.NoDevice.Description":"To set up HomeKit Secure Video, first enable iCloud for Home. On iOS, go to Settings #{chevron} %{fullName} #{chevron} iCloud and turn on Home. On a Mac, go to System Settings #{chevron} Apple Account #{chevron} iCloud, then select Home. Next, go to the Home app and turn on “Stream & Allow Recording” in Recording Options for your camera.","ContinueOnDevice.homeKitSecureVideo.NoDevice.Description2":"","ContinueOnDevice.homeKitSecureVideo.NoDevice.Notice":"Setting up HomeKit Secure Video requires a device running at least iOS 15, iPadOS 15, or macOS Monterey 12.","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.Organizer.NoDevice.Title":"How to Manage iCloud+ Family Sharing ","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.Organizer.NoDevice.Description":"Go to Settings #{chevron} %{fullName} #{chevron} iCloud #{chevron} iCloud Storage #{chevron} Family Usage","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.Organizer.NoDevice.Description2":"Go to System Settings #{chevron} Family Sharing #{chevron} iCloud Storage","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.OrganizerNoFamily.NoDevice.Title":"How to Start Sharing with Family","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.OrganizerNoFamily.NoDevice.Description":"Go to Settings #{chevron} %{fullName} #{chevron} iCloud #{chevron} iCloud Storage #{chevron} Share With Family","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.OrganizerNoFamily.NoDevice.Description2":"Go to System Settings #{chevron} Family Sharing #{chevron} iCloud Storage #{chevron} Share…","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.Member.NoDevice.Title":"How to Stop Using Shared iCloud+ Plan","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.Member.NoDevice.Description":"Go to Settings #{chevron} %{fullName} #{chevron} iCloud #{chevron} iCloud Storage #{chevron} Family Usage","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudPlusFamilySharing.Member.NoDevice.Description2":"Go to System Settings #{chevron} Family Sharing #{chevron} iCloud Storage","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudStorageManage.NoDevice.Title":"How to Manage Your iCloud Storage","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudStorageManage.NoDevice.Description":"Go to Settings #{chevron} %{fullName} #{chevron} iCloud #{chevron} iCloud Storage","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudStorageManage.NoDevice.Description2":"Go to System Settings #{chevron} Apple Account #{chevron} iCloud #{chevron} iCloud Storage: Manage","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudStorageManage.StorageFull.NoDevice.Title":"How to Change iCloud Plan and Add Storage","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudStorageManage.StorageFull.NoDevice.Description":"Go to Settings #{chevron} %{fullName} #{chevron} iCloud #{chevron} Manage Account Storage #{chevron} Change Storage Plan","ContinueOnDevice.iCloudStorageManage.StorageFull.NoDevice.Description2":"Go to System Settings #{chevron} Apple Account #{chevron} iCloud #{chevron} Manage #{chevron} Change Storage Plan","WebAccessBlocked.Greeting.0-6":"Good evening, %{firstName}.","WebAccessBlocked.Greeting.6-12":"Good morning, %{firstName}.","WebAccessBlocked.Greeting.12-18":"Good afternoon, %{firstName}.","WebAccessBlocked.Greeting.18-0":"Good evening, %{firstName}.","WebAccessBlocked.Greeting.Beneficiary":"%{firstName}’s iCloud","WebAccessBlocked.Greeting.Beneficiary.NameIsCJK":"%{firstName}’s iCloud","WebAccessBlocked.Title":"You Turned Off iCloud Data Web Access","WebAccessBlocked.Title.ADP":"iCloud Data Web Access is Off","WebAccessBlocked.Title.Sending":"Sending Notification to Your Devices…","WebAccessBlocked.Title.Failed":"Couldn’t Send Notification","WebAccessBlocked.Title.Sent":"Check the Notification on Your iPhone or iPad","WebAccessBlocked.Title.Beneficiary":"Can’t access %{firstName}’s data on %{currentDomain}","WebAccessBlocked.Title.Beneficiary.NameIsCJK":"Can’t access %{firstName}’s data on %{currentDomain}","WebAccessBlocked.Description":"To access data on %{currentDomain}, you’ll need to turn on web access in iCloud settings on your device.","WebAccessBlocked.Description.ADP":"You turned on Advanced Data Protection. To access data on %{currentDomain}, you’ll need to turn on web access in iCloud settings on your device.","WebAccessBlocked.Description.Failed":"There was a problem sending your notification.","WebAccessBlocked.Description.Sent":"The notification was sent to devices running iOS 16.2, or iPadOS 16.2, or later. Use it to go to iCloud settings and turn on “Access iCloud Data on the Web”.","WebAccessBlocked.Description2.Sent":"You can also turn on “Access iCloud Data on the Web” on a Mac running Ventura 13.1 or later. Go to System Settings #{chevron} %{fullName} #{chevron} iCloud.","WebAccessBlocked.Description.Beneficiary":"%{firstName} turned on Advanced Data Protection, so the data in %{firstName}’s account can only be accessed on an Apple device.","WebAccessBlocked.Description.Beneficiary.NameIsCJK":"%{firstName} turned on Advanced Data Protection, so the data in %{firstName}’s account can only be accessed on an Apple device.","WebAccessBlocked.NoDevice.Description":"Turn on “Access iCloud Data on the Web” in Settings #{chevron} %{fullName} #{chevron} iCloud","WebAccessBlocked.NoDevice.Description2":"Turn on “Access iCloud Data on the Web” in System Settings #{chevron} %{fullName} #{chevron} iCloud","WebAccessBlocked.NoDevice.Notice":"Requires a device running at least iOS 16.2, iPadOS 16.2 or macOS Ventura 13.1.","WebAccessBlocked.ManageButton.Title":"Manage on Device…","WebAccessBlocked.ManageButton.Title.SendAgain":"Send New Notification","We